title: Top Floor 1 Bedroom with Wood Burning Fireplace & Washer & Dryer!
posting_body: ['11216 18th Ave S, Tacoma , WA 98444', 'Miramonte is a small community nestled between Puyallup and Tacoma that gives residents the best of all worlds:', 'The location feels private, peaceful and serene, yet you’re just a few minutes from amazing shopping, dining and entertainment options.', 'With the Tacoma Mall, Lakewood Town Center, and South Hill Mall all within 15 minutes, everything you need can be found nearby.', 'We are also centrally located to PLU, Bates Technical College, and Clover Park Technical College, each of them being less than a 10 minute drive.', 'With easy access to the free way and a short drive to Joint Base Lewis-McChord, Miramonte has everything you need.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Large Gourmet Kitchen', 'Modern Color Schemes', 'Oversized Walk-In Closets', 'Wood Burning Fireplaces', 'Full Size Washer & Dryer', 'Community Features:', 'Dishwasher', 'Separate Dining Area', 'Large Closet', 'Walk-In Closet', 'Carpeted', 'Fireplace', 'In-Unit Laundry', 'Open-Concept', 'Spacious Floorplans', 'Views', 'Extra Storage', 'Private Balcony', 'Window Coverings', 'Cable Ready', 'Billiards Table', 'Cafe', 'Fitness Center', 'Pet Friendly', 'Recycling', 'Swimming Pool', 'Clubhouse', 'Night Patrol', 'Yoga Studio', 'Close to Public Transportation', 'Close to Shopping', 'Close to Airport', 'Close to Restaurants', 'Corporate Housing Available', 'Flexible Lease Terms Available', 'Close to Freeway', 'Close to Schools', 'Online Payments Available', 'Zero Deposit Community', 'Billiards Room', 'Resident Clubhouse', 'Flexible Monthly Payments with Flex Rent', 'Outdoor Fireside Lounge', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
